<h3 class="program-heading amos-about-header">About A Moment of Science</h3>

<div class="sidebar-lower-about program-block program-box">
	<p>A Moment of Science is a daily audio podcast, public radio program and video series providing the scientific story behind some of life's most perplexing mysteries. <a href="https://indianapublicmedia.org/amomentofscience/about.php">Learn More&nbsp;»</a></p>

</div>



